    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to find a new home for this absolute gem. Honestly, it is in such incredible shape that you'd swear it just left the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. It\u2019s sparkling clean and ready for your next big adventure. You\u2019ve really got to see it in person to appreciate how perfect it is\u2014feel free to reach out, I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
