    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to a standard that defies its previous ownership. This unit represents a rare opportunity to acquire a showroom-grade specimen, characterized by an unblemished exterior and a meticulously preserved interior. Rigorously inspected to ensure mechanical perfection, it stands as a testament to uncompromising care. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than the pinnacle of automotive excellence, this offering remains unparalleled in its class.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
