    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered icon. Featuring the high-revving 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing, the powerplant delivers linear torque and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, paired with a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a documented rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings. Finished in a preserved factory coat with zero oxidation, the exterior matches a cockpit free of bolster wear or pixel degradation in the instrument cluster. A true collector-grade specimen with a comprehensive service history and no mechanical deferred maintenance.",
